dct_title_s: Tunisie carte routière et touristique = Tunisia road map for tourists / conception, cartographie, filmographie, DIRASSET. (Recto)
dct_description_sm: Panel title. Relief shown by spot heights and isolines. Includes inset map of flight paths from Tunisia. Includes descriptive index to points of interest and two ancillary urban maps on verso. Insets: Tunis -- Île de Jerba.
